title: LThumbless v1 - Based on Sunaku's Layout v16 (Engrammer)
notes:
My Glove80 keymap [1], featuring the Engrammer layout [2] with Miryoku layers & home row mods [3], as discussed on Discord [4].

[1] https://sunaku.github.io/moergo-glove80-keyboard.html
[2] https://sunaku.github.io/engrammer-keyboard-layout.html
[3] https://sunaku.github.io/home-row-mods.html
[4] https://discord.com/channels/877392805654306816/1111469812850380831

Changes:
- Configuration: replaced `REGISTER_MODS_TERM` setting with `HOMEY_TAPPING_TERM` and `INDEX_TAPPING_TERM` similar to how things were back in v14.
- Miryoku: added `INDEX_TAPING_TERM` setting and changed hold-tap flavor from "balanced" to "tap-preferred" specifically for the index fingers. See https://discord.com/channels/877392805654306816/1111469812850380831/1133934078916300860
- Timing: decreased typing streak timeout from 175ms down to 160ms.
- Timing: increased home row mods registration timeout from 250ms to 260ms.
